rank(P)=rank(P(I-P-Q))\mbox{ and }rank(Q)=rank((I-P-Q)Q).
P(I-P-Q)=P-P^2-PQ=-PQ
(I-P-Q)Q=Q-PQ-Q^2=-PQ
rank(P)=rank(-PQ)=rank(Q).
